Package: pmxsimtools
Title: Various functions to aid simulation of pharmacometric models
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: c(person("Richard", "Hooijmaijers", email = "richardhooijmaijers@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre","cph")))
Description: The package includes functions to transform NONMEM models into R syntax so they can be used for
    simulations using the deSolve, RxODE or mrgsolve package. Furthermore functions are included to aid simulations performed
    directly in NONMEM
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.2)
Imports:
  MASS,
  whisker,
  plyr,
  cli
